											<DESC>
												<L-2 L="EN">Description: Represents an instance of an ARTI "Core" object, extending the EcucCoreDefinition. When using ARTI for debugging or hardware based tracing, this is mandatory (i.e. multiplicity 1..*), else optional.</L-2>
