													<SHORT-NAME>ArtiHardwareCoreInstanceLastErrorRef</SHORT-NAME>
													<DESC>
														<L-2 L="EN">Refers to the ArtiObjectInstanceParameter that contains the evaluation for the "last error" that happened on this core.</L-2>
													</DESC>
