													<SHORT-NAME>ArtiHardwareCoreInstanceRunningTaskPriorityRef</SHORT-NAME>
													<DESC>
														<L-2 L="EN">Refers to the ArtiObjectInstanceParameter that contains the evaluation for the "running task priority" that is on this core.</L-2>
													</DESC>
